articles.title: Hello world! Or Habr in English, v1.0
articles.subtitle: What new in JS in 2022?

paragraphs: This is the first post in our blog in 2019. And this is important for all of us: we are finally launching the English version of Habr! Actually it was ready in the middle of December, but — you know — releasing a new feature right before Christmas is like deploying on Friday afternoon. So we decided to do it in the beginning of 2019.
